channel.title: Global Walls
channel.description: Kinda something i never got into until lately, when i need it. What is a method used for Global Walls? Kinda like makeGlobalObject(xxxx, yyyy, objectid... you know the rest. I just dont know the change for it.

item.title: Global Walls
item.dc:creator: @cocoa cocoa
item.description:
